  "2370180": {
    "name": "Shrommzzz: Mushroom Foraging",
    "steam_appid": 2370180,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DEMO AVAILABLE!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Before you buy Shrommzzz please try the demo first! The game is not MacOS compatible and your graphics card needs to be DirectX 12 compatible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/6195fe6399e59a43faa2d883e4ba2f47.avif?t=1739630692\" width=600 height=250 /></span>Embark on a tranquil journey through 6 unique islands! Shrommzzz is the perfect hidden object game for fungi fans, devoted collectors and enthousiasts of exploring Mother nature’s wonderful landscapes. This vibrant adventure invites you to solve 105 mystifying riddles, which should give the completionists among us a whopping 15 hours of playtime. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/2b6ceb28ae790bd4429a788e1bc6c00a.poster.avif?t=1739630692\" width=284 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/2b6ceb28ae790bd4429a788e1bc6c00a.webm?t=1739630692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/2b6ceb28ae790bd4429a788e1bc6c00a.mp4?t=1739630692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shrommzzz Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore and Solve:</strong> Navigate and unlock beautifully crafted islands, solving riddles to discover mushrooms hidden away in all corners of the world. Take a cable car up the snowy mountain, poke around in glittering and mysterious caves, rummage through the shrubs or relax on the beach. Mushrooms could be anywhere! But beware, Dave won't be there to help you. Rumour has it that the new mushrooms make an angelic melody when you get closer, like the hot and cold game. And the bunnies... probably won't bother you... too much. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/e7b8a951469e698ac0d4abddfe6cf5bf.poster.avif?t=1739630692\" width=284 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/e7b8a951469e698ac0d4abddfe6cf5bf.webm?t=1739630692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/e7b8a951469e698ac0d4abddfe6cf5bf.mp4?t=1739630692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>When nighttime falls</strong>, you’ll uncover the knowledge left behind by a previous expedition through the remnants of their diary entries, only discoverable with your super special blacklight lantern. Each snippet offers a glimpse into the discoveries and experiences of those who walked the islands before you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/d2d0e45e82ee0424d48816f0fd943fc8.poster.avif?t=1739630692\" width=284 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/d2d0e45e82ee0424d48816f0fd943fc8.webm?t=1739630692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/d2d0e45e82ee0424d48816f0fd943fc8.mp4?t=1739630692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Farm and Create:</strong> Fung around by planting and matching mushroom spores to cultivate new variants. From real-life inspired mushrooms to wildly imaginative fungi, you’ll plant them all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/6765cb3dd4e0205fbb8f919bbf510e87.poster.avif?t=1739630692\" width=284 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/6765cb3dd4e0205fbb8f919bbf510e87.webm?t=1739630692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/6765cb3dd4e0205fbb8f919bbf510e87.mp4?t=1739630692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Decorate and Design:</strong> Express your creativity by decorating Basecamp Island with charming lamps, sculptures, cute benches, archways with or without stringlights... How do you afford all of this? By selling mushrooms, of course!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/040ec351fe2d8fea21c99ca42b20a049.poster.avif?t=1739630692\" width=284 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/040ec351fe2d8fea21c99ca42b20a049.webm?t=1739630692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/040ec351fe2d8fea21c99ca42b20a049.mp4?t=1739630692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shrommzzz Ambience</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shrommzzz dazzles with its bright, saturated colors and round, friendly designs. Immerse yourself in a world free of music but alive with the constant, soothing sounds of nature—birds tweeting, bees buzzing, rain clattering, waves crashing, storms brewing, frogs chirping, leaves rustling and so much more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/b6900825a7740136e6423ba60f5dd8e3.poster.avif?t=1739630692\" width=284 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/b6900825a7740136e6423ba60f5dd8e3.webm?t=1739630692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/b6900825a7740136e6423ba60f5dd8e3.mp4?t=1739630692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game offers a relaxing escape into nature, perfect for unwinding after a long day. Whether you're exploring, farming, or simply decorating, every aspect of Shrommzzz is designed to soothe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/5374784acbb9a61ef8f0f7404821d2ea.poster.avif?t=1739630692\" width=284 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/5374784acbb9a61ef8f0f7404821d2ea.webm?t=1739630692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/5374784acbb9a61ef8f0f7404821d2ea.mp4?t=1739630692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join Our Community:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We cherish every adventurer’s presence. Join our Discord to share experiences, tips, and peaceful moments with fellow mushroom foragers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/f8f02179182a46c0669c99552769bde4.poster.avif?t=1739630692\" width=284 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/f8f02179182a46c0669c99552769bde4.webm?t=1739630692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/f8f02179182a46c0669c99552769bde4.mp4?t=1739630692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Developed with Love:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafted with care by a dedicated duo of developers, they invite you to lose yourself in a world of subtle wonders. Enter the serene realm of Shrommzzz and let the mysteries of mushrooms unfold at your own pace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Psssst:   Gra jest teraz dostępna również w języku polskim! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vanaf nu is het spel ook beschikbaar in het Nederlands!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/d0cf3a54e6b04611d25bbf7749be948c.poster.avif?t=1739630692\" width=284 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/d0cf3a54e6b04611d25bbf7749be948c.webm?t=1739630692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370180/extras/d0cf3a54e6b04611d25bbf7749be948c.mp4?t=1739630692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
